front.title: •It's A Trap!
front.gametext: USED: Cancel Sniper or Blasted Droid.  LOST: Use 3 Force to cancel any battle just initiated at a site. (Immune to Sense.)
front.lore: Luke's decision to ignore Leia's warning about the trap cost him an arm and a. . . well, just a hand actually.

combo: It's A Trap! + All My Urchins A good way to make your opponent lose 2 Force for nothing. (l000needles)
cancels: Any battle just initiated at a site
